nodes.beat: Jack, a young and curious boy living in a small town, receives a handful of magic beans from a mysterious old man.
Jack's mother, skeptical about the magic beans, throws them out the window.
Overnight, a giant beanstalk grows from the beans, reaching up to the clouds.
Jack, filled with curiosity, decides to climb the beanstalk.
Jack encounters a giant's castle in the sky and sneaks in.
He discovers the giant's treasures, including a goose that lays golden eggs.
Jack steals the goose and makes a narrow escape as the giant chases him.
Jack chops down the beanstalk, causing the giant to fall to his death.
Jack and his mother live happily ever after with the wealth from the golden eggs.
Disappointed with the beans, Jack decides to sell them online.
Jack encounters a giant's castle in the sky and films it for his vlog.
He discovers the giant's treasures, including a magical harp that plays on its own.
Jack steals the harp and narrowly escapes as the giant chases him.
Jack becomes an internet sensation, and his vlogs provide a comfortable life for him and his mother.
Jack, a young and adventurous boy, discovers a handful of old beans in his grandmother's attic.
Jack encounters a giant's castle in the sky and decides to explore it.
He discovers the giant's treasures, including a magical mirror that shows the future.
Jack steals the mirror and makes a narrow escape as the giant chases him.
Jack and his mother use the mirror's power to help their town and live happily ever after.
He discovers the giant's treasures, including a magical sword with immense power.
Jack steals the sword and narrowly escapes as the giant chases him.
Jack becomes a local hero, and his adventures provide a comfortable life for him and his mother.
